title: OpenBSD 5.6/amd64 (x86_64)
description:
This is OpenBSD 5.6/amd64 (64-bit x86_64)

Built from CVS release sources. Official release date: 2014-11-01.

ISO File size: 552,275,968 bytes
MD5 (openbsd-5.6-amd64.iso) = 1bfb3605875b877c73b0b1fd5de02029

CD is bootable and contains the amd64 distribution + complete sources.

New features in OpenBSD 5.6: see http://www.openbsd.org/56.html

Unlike the offical distribution, this one has all security fixes up
to 2014-10-22 already compiled in: http://www.openbsd.org/errata56.html
